    <!-- Content Section -->
    <div class="content-section">
        When planning an event, choosing between a gala dinner and a dinner and dance can set the tone for the evening. Though both feature dining and entertainment, they cater to different purposes and atmospheres. Here’s how to distinguish between the two and select the right format for your occasion.
    </div>

